		<div class = "text">
			In an effort to improve my visual design skills, I decided to try my hand at #the100dayproject, an online campaign that encourages folks to dedicate themselves to a craft for one hundred days. Currently, I am still working towards my 100th day! You can check out my progress <a target = "_blank" class = "link" href="https://instagram.com/jbaek100/">here</a>.
